<section id="about" class="feature">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="primary_info">
      <h1>
        <em>爱代码就像爱生命</em>
        <h2>编程乐趣，就在 “我们的代码公园”</h2>
      </h1>

      <p>你可以 · 记录你的代码，</p>并分享给他人 · 留下你的声音，</p>让世界听得见 · 找到你的知己，</p>一起学习成长· 帮助别人，</p>快乐自己，从这里开始 
      </p>

      <p>
        <%= link_to '&raquo; 开始录制'.html_safe, docs_path(:record) %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="secondary_info" style="height:400px">
      <%= player @asciicast, :speed => 1.0, :hud => false if @asciicast %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="supplimental">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="main">
      <h1>Recent Asciicasts</h1>
      <%= render :partial => 'asciicasts/previews',
                 :locals => { :asciicasts => @asciicasts } %>
    </div>

    <div class="extras">
      <%= render :partial => 'shared/browse_categories' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
